description: Wasteland is proud to present “Into The Mist” a BDSM themed soap opera with a supernatural twist. In the fifth episode of this series, Victoria’s nephew, Brad, is to arrive and Melissa will finally assume her duties as his governess. Or will she? Brad is, needless to say, not what she had expected! Brad immediately gets on his aunt’s negative side when it becomes clear that he has some secrets of his own. Nephew, he might be, but no one is safe from trips to the punishment room, as Brad quickly finds out. But Grayson is not happy either, and Victoria finds, to her horror, that she can be taken to the punishment room herself. (Episode 5 of 9)
title: Into the Mist - Episode 5: Who Is Brad?
